### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/tasks

### Add a New Task
POST http://localhost:3000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Sample Task",
    "status": "Pending"
}

### Update a Task
PUT http://localhost:3000/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Completed"
}

### Delete a Task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/tasks/1
